  "title": "A round multicolored UFO hovered over Guará I &#8211; DF [2001]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/13/a-round-multicolored-ufo-hovered-over-guara-i-df-2001/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-pK",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 17th, 2001</strong>. Time: 9:00 pm. Duration: 2 nights in a row. A witness residing in Guará I, Distrito Federal, spotted a large, unidentified flying object in the shape of a balloon emitting several strong colors. According to the witness&#8217;s account, the UFO was stationary and remained this way most of the time. The sighting took place two nights in a row in Guará I. The UFO was seen with the naked eye in good visibility, and no condensation trails were observed.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.593. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni no Guará I, Brasília, Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
